title: 2012 O'Neill Epic Wetsuit
description: The 2012 Epic Series now with many of the same sick features as our high-end wetsuits. FluidFlex™ Firewall chest, double seal neck closure, LSD (lumbar seamless design) and re-engineered covert blackout zip. Clean graphics and sharp style lines make the Epic the best value in the industry.
